<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541000' id='t-541000'>We heard there was a woman doctor who was treating people.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543000' id='t-543000'>I walked 10 kilometers, putting one foot in front of the other.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='546000' id='t-546000'>I got there and I saw huge crowds.</span>
