</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:29
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558000' id='t-558000'>I had to crawl in between the legs of these people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561000' id='t-561000'>with my sister strapped on my back,</span>
