<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='566000' id='t-566000'>And while they were trying to break down the door,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='569000' id='t-569000'>I climbed in through the window, and jumped in.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573000' id='t-573000'>This woman told me it was in the nick of time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='576000' id='t-576000'>By the time we jumped into that hall, she was barely moving.</span>
