<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633000' id='t-633000'>Why am I telling that? I'm telling you that because --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635000' id='t-635000'>when it is you or your person involved --</span>
