<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='654000' id='t-654000'>You just want the person to be alive!</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='659000' id='t-659000'>And now let me become less sentimental, and say that saving lives --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='662000' id='t-662000'>which some of the aid we get does on this continent --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665000' id='t-665000'>when you save the life of anyone, a farmer, a teacher, a mother,</span>
