<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810000' id='t-810000'>When we ask them and tell them what we need,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='821000' id='t-821000'>one of my worries today is that we have many foundations now.</span>
