<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='885000' id='t-885000'>And many times I get the impression that they are not really even interested</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='887000' id='t-887000'>in hearing from Africans who might know.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='891000' id='t-891000'>They want to visit us,</span>
