<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1016000' id='t-1016000'>I firmly believe in that private sector thing too.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1020000' id='t-1020000'>But it cannot do it alone.</span>
